sources.title: 1941 Was Geschah In Dieser Nacht ( Karl Ludwig Diehl, Hans Brausewetter, Theo Lingen, Lucie Englisch, Irene Von Meyendorff)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1941. Was geschah in dieser Nacht.  U.a mit Theo Lingen und Karl Ludwig Diehl

metadata.Plot: Since Marion feels ill-treated by her boyfriend her friend Julia confronts him in his home only to learn that she is scolding the wrong guy: there are two cousins named Johannes sharing the apartment. And this Johannes is charming...
metadata.Writer: Nikolaus Asztalos, Franz Gribitz, János Vaszary
metadata.Actors: Lili Muráti, Irene von Meyendorff, Lucie Englisch
